OL,7,FParents were promised the #35-a-ticket
OL,8,Fevent at Box Hub in was "a journey
OL,9,Ffilled with wondrous creations and
OL,10,Fenchanting surprises at every turn"
OL,11,Fbefore police were called upon the
OL,12,F"shambolic" reality of the event.
OL,14,FThe warehouse, it turned out, was half
OL,15,Fempty, as one parents described it on
OL,16,FFacebook as "a very simple set up with
OL,17,Fcheap backdrops around it."
