OL,7,FThe event, where children were
OL,8,Freportedly given some jelly babies and
OL,9,Flemonade, was axed after just half a
OL,10,Fday and the police being called.
OL,12,FThe warehouse was half empty and
OL,13,Fdescribed as 'a very simple set-up
OL,14,Fwith cheap backdrops around it'
OL,15,F(Credit: Maryanne McCormack)
OL,17,FPolice Scotland said officers were
OL,18,Fcalled and "advice was given", but the
OL,19,Fsituation was not a police matter.
