OL,7,FBox Hub said in a statement: "As a
OL,8,FVenue Hire company we first came into
OL,9,Fcontact with the event organisers -
OL,10,F'House of Illuminati' - in January.
OL,12,F"The company detailed plans for an
OL,13,Fimmersive and captivating family
OL,14,Fevent. The event itself did not
OL,15,Freflect what had been promised to the
OL,16,Fmany paying customers and was
OL,17,Fincredibly underwhelming.
